author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Tech-Value H1 net profit rises to 264,654 euros
text:
Sept 29 Tech-Value SpA :
* Reported on Monday H1 net profit of 264,654 euros ($298,212.13) versus 164,060 euros a year ago
* H1 revenues of 4.5 million euros versus 3.6 million euros a year ago
